      "content": "counseling doesn't change the fact that i'm ruined. i've tried talking to people but they just look at me like i'm a failure. it's not just about the money, it's the feeling that there's no version of the future where this isn't heavy. it's like i'm just stuck in this loop of misery and it's never gonna stop. i'm just so tired of fighting it.",
